messages.message: Question on KonMari week - how will participation be accounted for? Are there plans in place to ensure that everyone (or mostly everyone I assume) participates? cc @John Hung

It'll be mandatory and taken into account in OKR planning and budgeting. More details in this plan (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ko35nto44PvSShEDX3y2t4pO-LL5nm9Hm3y0aZUt-R4/edit) that I aim to finalize by end of this week after getting more feedback.
